            <description><![CDATA[<h2>TokenBar 0.18.4</h2>
<h3>Highlights</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix a first-relaunch launch crash caused by hidden keepalive-window constraint updates on startup/reopen.</li>
<li>Prevent accidental menu card activation on double-click by ignoring multi-click gesture events.</li>
<li>Stabilize CI Linux CLI builds by clearing stale SwiftPM binary artifact cache before build steps.</li>
<li>Align lint configuration with repo style by disabling <code>sortImports</code> and resolving strict lint blockers.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/tokenbar/tokenbar/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">View full changelog</a></p>
]]></description>
